\f0\b  
\f2\b0 Set all channels to this float value. This command is asynchronous.\
	\

\f0\b set(...values) 
\f2\b0 - A list of values for each channel of the control bus.  The list of values supplied should not be greater than the number of channels. This command is asynchronous.\
\

\f0\b setn(values) 
\f2\b0 - As 
\f0\b set
\f2\b0  but takes an array as an argument.\
